<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.2.8">
<l>toṇṭellām niṉṉaṭi yētoḻu tuyyumā</l>
<l>kaṇṭutāṉ kaṇṇapu rantoḻap pōyiṉāḷ</l>
<l>vaṇṭulāṅ kōtaiyeṉ pētai maṇiniṟam</l>
<l>koṇṭutāṉ kōyiṉmai ceyvatu takkatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Seeing the way that all the devotees worshipping at your feet are saved,</l>
<l>She herself went to worship in Kaṇṇapuram.</l>
<l>Taking the beautiful complexion from my simple girl,</l>
<l>With a garland where bees wander, is your acting ignobly proper?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
